name: QEWE Ransomware Encrypted File
summary: A file with the .qewe extension has been maliciously renamed and encrypted by QEWE ransomware . It contains a document, image, video, or other file the ransomware is holding hostage. The .qewe extension is added to the file's normal extension, producing a compound extension like .jpg.qewe .
